 "title": "Foundation — The Operating System Behind the Words",
 "objective": null,
 "primaryKpi": null,
 "intro": "<h2>Foundation &mdash; The Operating System Behind the Words</h2>\n\n<div class=\"submenu\">\n  <a href=\"#core-principle\">Core Principle</a>\n  <a href=\"#six-objectives\">Six Objectives</a>\n  <a href=\"#process-map\">8-Step Process</a>\n  <a href=\"#journey\">Customer Journey</a>\n  <a href=\"#scorecard\">Invisible Scorecard</a>\n  <a href=\"#ladder\">Mastery Ladder</a>\n  <a href=\"#how-to-read\">How To Read This</a>\n  <a href=\"#legend\">Module Key</a>\n</div>",
 "sections": [
  {
   "slug": "the-core-principle",
   "title": "The Core Principle",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"core-principle\">The Core Principle</h3>\n\n<div class=\"pull\">\n  Sales is not persuasion. Sales is the systematic reduction of uncertainty.<br>\n  We do not sell repairs. We manufacture certainty &mdash; and certainty buys repairs by itself.\n</div>\n\n<p>Every customer who calls a shop is operating in a fog. They are uncertain whether the noise is dangerous,\nuncertain whether they are about to be taken advantage of, uncertain whether the price will be fair, uncertain\nwhether the shop can be trusted, uncertain about their car, uncertain about themselves. <strong>That fog is the\nreal problem we solve.</strong> Repairs are simply the byproduct.</p>\n\n<p>The advisor&rsquo;s job is to be the lighthouse. Each of the eight steps in this system removes one specific\nkind of uncertainty. When all eight are removed, the customer doesn&rsquo;t feel sold &mdash; they feel\n<em>guided</em>. And guided customers come back, refer their friends, and never haggle.</p>\n\n<!-- Uncertainty-to-Certainty Arc -->\n<div class=\"figure\">\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 720 220\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Uncertainty to certainty arc\">\n    <defs>\n      <linearGradient id=\"arcGrad\" x1=\"0\" x2=\"1\">\n        <stop offset=\"0\" stop-color=\"#B7332A\"/>\n        <stop offset=\"0.5\" stop-color=\"#C8A75C\"/>\n        <stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"#1B3358\"/>\n      </linearGradient>\n    </defs>\n    <!-- arc -->\n    <path d=\"M 40 170 Q 360 -40 680 170\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"url(#arcGrad)\" stroke-width=\"6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    <!-- endpoints -->\n    <circle cx=\"40\"  cy=\"170\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#B7332A\"/>\n    <circle cx=\"680\" cy=\"170\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#1B3358\"/>\n    <!-- labels at start -->\n    <text x=\"40\"  y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#B7332A\">CUSTOMER ENTERS</text>\n    <text x=\"40\"  y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#4A4A4A\">Uncertain &middot; Fearful &middot; Defensive</text>\n    <!-- labels at end -->\n    <text x=\"680\" y=\"200\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#1B3358\">CUSTOMER LEAVES</text>\n    <text x=\"680\" y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#4A4A4A\">Educated &middot; Confident &middot; Loyal</text>\n    <!-- step ticks along arc -->\n    <g font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#1B3358\">\n      <circle cx=\"120\" cy=\"115\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"120\" y=\"119\" text-anchor=\"middle\">1</text>\n      <circle cx=\"200\" cy=\"70\"  r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"200\" y=\"74\" text-anchor=\"middle\">2</text>\n      <circle cx=\"290\" cy=\"40\"  r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"290\" y=\"44\" text-anchor=\"middle\">3</text>\n      <circle cx=\"360\" cy=\"32\"  r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"360\" y=\"36\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4</text>\n      <circle cx=\"430\" cy=\"40\"  r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"430\" y=\"44\" text-anchor=\"middle\">5</text>\n      <circle cx=\"520\" cy=\"70\"  r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"520\" y=\"74\" text-anchor=\"middle\">6</text>\n      <circle cx=\"600\" cy=\"115\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"600\" y=\"119\" text-anchor=\"middle\">7</text>\n      <circle cx=\"660\" cy=\"150\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#FAF4E4\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><text x=\"660\" y=\"154\" text-anchor=\"middle\">8</text>\n    </g>\n  </svg>\n  <div class=\"caption\">Figure 0.1 &middot; The Certainty Arc &mdash; eight steps, one direction</div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "the-six-sales-objectives",
   "title": "The Six Sales Objectives",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"six-objectives\">The Six Sales Objectives</h3>\n\n<p>Underneath the 8 process steps live 6 unchanging objectives. Every move an advisor makes &mdash; every word,\npause, walk, and inspection &mdash; must serve at least one of these. If a behavior doesn&rsquo;t serve one of the\nsix, it&rsquo;s waste motion. Coach against it.</p>\n\n<div class=\"grid-3\">\n  <div class=\"card gold-top\"><span class=\"badge\">OBJ 1</span><h4>Build Relationship</h4>\n    <p>Make a friend. Become the human the customer trusts before they trust the shop.</p></div>\n  <div class=\"card gold-top\"><span class=\"badge\">OBJ 2</span><h4>Get Custody</h4>\n    <p>The car in our bay is the only car we can save. Custody is the gate to every other objective.</p></div>\n  <div class=\"card gold-top\"><span class=\"badge\">OBJ 3</span><h4>Separate Customer From Vehicle</h4>\n    <p>Emotional distance from the car allows logical decisions. Loaners, shuttles, and lobby comfort do real selling work.</p></div>\n  <div class=\"card gold-top\"><span class=\"badge\">OBJ 4</span><h4>Identify True Vehicle Health</h4>\n    <p>A complete, honest, documented picture. The DVI is our X-ray.</p></div>\n  <div class=\"card gold-top\"><span class=\"badge\">OBJ 5</span><h4>Educate the Customer</h4>\n    <p>An informed customer is a confident customer. A confident customer authorizes work.</p></div>\n  <div class=\"card gold-top\"><span class=\"badge\">OBJ 6</span><h4>Deliver a Safe &amp; Reliable Vehicle</h4>\n    <p>The repair is the receipt. The relationship is the asset.</p></div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "the-8-step-sales-process-map",
   "title": "The 8-Step Sales Process Map",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"process-map\">The 8-Step Sales Process Map</h3>\n\n<p>The steps run in order. They are not menu items. Skipping a step doesn&rsquo;t save time &mdash; it forces a\nre-do later in the call (or worse, kills the sale). Each step has its own objective, its own psychology, its own\nmastery checks, and its own KPIs. Every module in this curriculum is built around one step.</p>\n\n<!-- Process Map SVG — refined -->\n<div class=\"figure\">\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 760 320\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Eight-step process map\">\n    <defs>\n      <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"8\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" orient=\"auto\">\n        <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/>\n      </marker>\n      <filter id=\"ps-shadow\" x=\"-20%\" y=\"-20%\" width=\"140%\" height=\"140%\">\n        <feDropShadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"2\" stdDeviation=\"2\" flood-color=\"#1B3358\" flood-opacity=\"0.16\"/>\n      </filter>\n    </defs>\n    <g font-family=\"Helvetica\">\n      <!-- Row 1: Steps 1-4 -->\n      <g filter=\"url(#ps-shadow)\">\n        <rect x=\"20\"  y=\"30\" width=\"170\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1B3358\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <rect x=\"210\" y=\"30\" width=\"170\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1B3358\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <rect x=\"400\" y=\"30\" width=\"170\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1B3358\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <rect x=\"590\" y=\"30\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1B3358\" rx=\"6\"/>\n      </g>\n      <!-- Step badges (number circles in corner) -->\n      <circle cx=\"42\" cy=\"52\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"42\" y=\"57\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">1</text>\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">RAPPORT</text>\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">ESTABLISH</text>\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"94\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">make a friend</text>\n\n      <circle cx=\"232\" cy=\"52\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"232\" y=\"57\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">2</text>\n      <text x=\"305\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">CREDIBILITY</text>\n      <text x=\"305\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">ESTABLISH</text>\n      <text x=\"305\" y=\"94\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">build authority</text>\n\n      <circle cx=\"422\" cy=\"52\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"422\" y=\"57\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">3</text>\n      <text x=\"495\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">CUSTODY</text>\n      <text x=\"495\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">COLLECT DATA</text>\n      <text x=\"495\" y=\"94\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">get the car</text>\n\n      <circle cx=\"612\" cy=\"52\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"612\" y=\"57\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">4</text>\n      <text x=\"675\" y=\"62\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">INSPECT</text>\n      <text x=\"675\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">&amp; ANALYZE</text>\n      <text x=\"675\" y=\"94\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">DVI = X-ray</text>\n\n      <!-- Arrows row 1 -->\n      <line x1=\"190\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"206\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n      <line x1=\"380\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"396\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n      <line x1=\"570\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"586\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n      <!-- U-turn from step 4 to step 5 -->\n      <path d=\"M 740 110 Q 760 160, 740 200\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n      <!-- Row 2: Steps 5-8 (going right-to-left, lighter navy to indicate \"back half\") -->\n      <g filter=\"url(#ps-shadow)\">\n        <rect x=\"20\"  y=\"200\" width=\"170\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#2C4A75\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <rect x=\"210\" y=\"200\" width=\"170\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#2C4A75\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <rect x=\"400\" y=\"200\" width=\"170\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#2C4A75\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <rect x=\"590\" y=\"200\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#2C4A75\" rx=\"6\"/>\n      </g>\n\n      <circle cx=\"612\" cy=\"222\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"612\" y=\"227\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">5</text>\n      <text x=\"675\" y=\"232\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">STRATEGIZE</text>\n      <text x=\"675\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">BUILD &amp;</text>\n      <text x=\"675\" y=\"264\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">run the bases</text>\n\n      <circle cx=\"422\" cy=\"222\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"422\" y=\"227\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">6</text>\n      <text x=\"495\" y=\"232\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">PRESENT</text>\n      <text x=\"495\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">EDUCATE</text>\n      <text x=\"495\" y=\"264\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">10-step ISO</text>\n\n      <circle cx=\"232\" cy=\"222\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"232\" y=\"227\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">7</text>\n      <text x=\"305\" y=\"232\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">OBJECTIONS</text>\n      <text x=\"305\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">OVERCOME</text>\n      <text x=\"305\" y=\"264\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">8 boss battles</text>\n\n      <circle cx=\"42\" cy=\"222\" r=\"14\" fill=\"#C8A75C\"/><text x=\"42\" y=\"227\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#1B3358\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"800\">8</text>\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"232\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#C8A75C\" font-size=\"8.5\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-weight=\"600\">CLOSE</text>\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">EXECUTE</text>\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"264\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFF\" font-size=\"9\" font-style=\"italic\">direction-facing</text>\n\n      <!-- Arrows row 2 (right to left) -->\n      <line x1=\"590\" y1=\"240\" x2=\"574\" y2=\"240\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n      <line x1=\"400\" y1=\"240\" x2=\"384\" y2=\"240\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n      <line x1=\"210\" y1=\"240\" x2=\"194\" y2=\"240\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3.5\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n      <!-- end indicator -->\n      <text x=\"115\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"9\" font-weight=\"700\" fill=\"#A78743\" letter-spacing=\"1.5\">&rarr; AUTHORIZED &amp; LOYAL CUSTOMER</text>\n    </g>\n  </svg>\n  <div class=\"caption\">Figure 0.2 &middot; The 8-step flow &mdash; the only correct order. Top row builds trust; bottom row closes.</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Step Table -->\n<table class=\"matrix\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th style=\"width:5%\">#</th><th style=\"width:22%\">Step</th><th>Primary Objective</th><th>Uncertainty Removed</th><th>Leading KPI</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr><td>1</td><td><strong>Establish Rapport</strong></td><td>Make a friend</td><td>&ldquo;Are these people safe?&rdquo;</td><td>Greet-to-tour conversion</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>2</td><td><strong>Establish Credibility</strong></td><td>Build authority</td><td>&ldquo;Do they know what they&rsquo;re doing?&rdquo;</td><td>Tour-to-DVI consent</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>3</td><td><strong>Collect Data</strong></td><td>Get custody</td><td>&ldquo;What&rsquo;s actually wrong?&rdquo;</td><td>Inquiry-to-RO conversion</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>4</td><td><strong>Inspect &amp; Analyze</strong></td><td>Identify true vehicle health</td><td>&ldquo;How bad is it really?&rdquo;</td><td>% DVIs completed within 90 min</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>5</td><td><strong>Build &amp; Strategize</strong></td><td>Sequence the conversation</td><td>&ldquo;Where do we start?&rdquo;</td><td>% calls with proper base order</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>6</td><td><strong>Present</strong></td><td>Educate the customer</td><td>&ldquo;Why does this matter?&rdquo;</td><td>DVI view-rate &amp; PRS adherence</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>7</td><td><strong>Overcome Objections</strong></td><td>Resolve hesitation</td><td>&ldquo;Should I really do this?&rdquo;</td><td>1st-objection close rate</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>8</td><td><strong>Execute / Close</strong></td><td>Deliver commitment</td><td>&ldquo;What happens next?&rdquo;</td><td>Authorized &divide; presented</td></tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "the-customers-internal-journey",
   "title": "The Customer’s Internal Journey",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"journey\">The Customer&rsquo;s Internal Journey</h3>\n\n<p>Sales is two parallel tracks: what the advisor <em>does</em> and what the customer <em>feels</em>. The\nadvisor controls the first. The second is the actual scoreboard. Track both.</p>\n\n<table class=\"matrix\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>Step</th><th>Advisor Action</th><th>Customer&rsquo;s Inner Voice (Before)</th><th>Customer&rsquo;s Inner Voice (After)</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr><td>1 Rapport</td><td>Smile, pause, &ldquo;Right place.&rdquo;</td><td><em>&ldquo;Am I about to get hustled?&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;Okay, this person seems normal.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>2 Credibility</td><td>Shop tour, ASE, warranty, transport.</td><td><em>&ldquo;Do they even know what they&rsquo;re doing?&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;These guys are legit.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>3 Custody</td><td>Keys + boom board + concern documented.</td><td><em>&ldquo;What if it&rsquo;s something huge?&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;At least it&rsquo;s in good hands.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>4 Inspect</td><td>Full DVI, photos, video, tech sync.</td><td><em>&ldquo;Are they going to invent stuff?&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;Wow, they actually looked at everything.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>5 Strategize</td><td>Sequence Good-Good-Bad, set bases.</td><td>(unseen)</td><td>(unseen)</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>6 Present</td><td>PRS, video, micro-commitments.</td><td><em>&ldquo;Is this real or upsell?&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;I see exactly what they see.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>7 Objections</td><td>Listen, reframe, payment options.</td><td><em>&ldquo;I&rsquo;m not sure I want to do this.&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;That actually makes sense.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>8 Close</td><td>Assumptive close, direction-facing.</td><td><em>&ldquo;Did I just agree to spend that?&rdquo;</em></td><td>&ldquo;Glad it&rsquo;s handled.&rdquo;</td></tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "the-invisible-scorecard",
   "title": "The Invisible Scorecard",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"scorecard\">The Invisible Scorecard</h3>\n\n<p>Every customer silently grades the advisor on three traits, in this order. Score all three and price becomes\nirrelevant. Lose any one and price becomes the only conversation that ever happens.</p>\n\n<!-- Trust Triangle SVG — fixed (labels outside circles to prevent text overflow) -->\n<div class=\"figure\">\n  <svg viewBox=\"0 0 700 480\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Trust triangle\">\n    <defs>\n      <linearGradient id=\"tt-fill\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"0\" y2=\"1\">\n        <stop offset=\"0\" stop-color=\"#FAF4E4\"/>\n        <stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"#F0E2BE\"/>\n      </linearGradient>\n      <filter id=\"tt-shadow\" x=\"-30%\" y=\"-30%\" width=\"160%\" height=\"160%\">\n        <feDropShadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"3\" stdDeviation=\"3\" flood-color=\"#1B3358\" flood-opacity=\"0.20\"/>\n      </filter>\n    </defs>\n\n    <!-- background triangle -->\n    <polygon points=\"350,110 100,380 600,380\" fill=\"url(#tt-fill)\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n\n    <!-- inner subtle guide -->\n    <polygon points=\"350,160 170,360 530,360\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" stroke-dasharray=\"3 5\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n\n    <!-- center label -->\n    <text x=\"350\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"38\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#1B3358\" letter-spacing=\"4\">TRUST</text>\n    <text x=\"350\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#4A4A4A\" font-style=\"italic\">= permission to advise</text>\n\n    <!-- ====== TOP VERTEX — COMPETENCE (label ABOVE circle, on cream paper) ====== -->\n    <text x=\"350\" y=\"26\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"9\" letter-spacing=\"3\" fill=\"#A78743\" font-weight=\"700\">TRAIT 1</text>\n    <text x=\"350\" y=\"55\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#1B3358\">COMPETENCE</text>\n    <text x=\"350\" y=\"74\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#4A4A4A\" font-style=\"italic\">\"Do they know what they're doing?\"</text>\n    <!-- Circle with just the number -->\n    <g filter=\"url(#tt-shadow)\">\n      <circle cx=\"350\" cy=\"110\" r=\"22\" fill=\"#1B3358\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n    </g>\n    <text x=\"350\" y=\"119\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"22\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#C8A75C\">1</text>\n\n    <!-- ====== BOTTOM-LEFT — TRANSPARENT (label BELOW circle) ====== -->\n    <g filter=\"url(#tt-shadow)\">\n      <circle cx=\"100\" cy=\"380\" r=\"22\" fill=\"#1B3358\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n    </g>\n    <text x=\"100\" y=\"389\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"22\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#C8A75C\">2</text>\n    <text x=\"100\" y=\"422\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"9\" letter-spacing=\"3\" fill=\"#A78743\" font-weight=\"700\">TRAIT 2</text>\n    <text x=\"100\" y=\"448\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"19\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#1B3358\">TRANSPARENT</text>\n    <text x=\"100\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#4A4A4A\" font-style=\"italic\">\"Are they hiding anything?\"</text>\n\n    <!-- ====== BOTTOM-RIGHT — TRUSTWORTHY (label BELOW circle) ====== -->\n    <g filter=\"url(#tt-shadow)\">\n      <circle cx=\"600\" cy=\"380\" r=\"22\" fill=\"#1B3358\" stroke=\"#C8A75C\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n    </g>\n    <text x=\"600\" y=\"389\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"22\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#C8A75C\">3</text>\n    <text x=\"600\" y=\"422\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"9\" letter-spacing=\"3\" fill=\"#A78743\" font-weight=\"700\">TRAIT 3</text>\n    <text x=\"600\" y=\"448\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"19\" font-weight=\"800\" fill=\"#1B3358\">TRUSTWORTHY</text>\n    <text x=\"600\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Helvetica\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#4A4A4A\" font-style=\"italic\">\"Would they do this for family?\"</text>\n  </svg>\n  <div class=\"caption\">Figure 0.3 &middot; The Trust Triangle &mdash; three legs, no shortcuts. Score all three &rarr; price is irrelevant. Lose any one &rarr; price is the only conversation.</div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "the-mastery-ladder",
   "title": "The Mastery Ladder",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"ladder\">The Mastery Ladder</h3>\n\n<p>Promotion is not a calendar event. It is an evidence-based gate. Every advisor moves through five levels\non observable behavior &mdash; not tenure, not opinion, not vibes.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"step-list\">\n  <li><strong>Level 1 &middot; Rookie</strong>Reads scripts. Survives calls. No improvisation. Goal: don&rsquo;t lose a customer.</li>\n  <li><strong>Level 2 &middot; Advisor</strong>Runs scripts naturally. Identifies concern vs. symptom. Books appointments without quoting.</li>\n  <li><strong>Level 3 &middot; Closer</strong>Owns East-West. Runs the bases in order. PRS by heart. Customers feel informed, not sold.</li>\n  <li><strong>Level 4 &middot; Pro</strong>Defeats all 8 Boss Battles. Re-opens missed sales. Coaches Rookies in their downtime.</li>\n  <li><strong>Level 5 &middot; Champion</strong>Customers request by name. Builds the book. Trains other advisors. Owns culture.</li>\n</ul>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "how-to-read-this-book",
   "title": "How to Read This Book",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"how-to-read\">How to Read This Book</h3>\n\n<div class=\"grid-2\">\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h4>If you&rsquo;re an Advisor</h4>\n    <p>Read one module per week. Drill twice a day. Don&rsquo;t skip the &ldquo;Psychology Decoder&rdquo; sections &mdash;\n    those are how scripts stop sounding scripted. Pass the Mastery Check before you advance.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h4>If you&rsquo;re a Coach / Manager</h4>\n    <p>Read the &ldquo;Coach&rsquo;s Corner&rdquo; in every module first. That tells you what to listen for on ride-alongs,\n    what to score, and what to praise vs. what to correct. Then read the KPI section to know what counts.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h4>If you&rsquo;re an Owner</h4>\n    <p>Read the Foundation and the Coach&rsquo;s OS appendix. Then audit one advisor against the Invisible Scorecard\n    this week. You&rsquo;ll find the leak in your close rate inside 30 minutes.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <h4>If you&rsquo;re a Trainer</h4>\n    <p>Use the modules as a workshop. Each one is a 60&ndash;90 minute session: 15 min teach, 30 min drill, 15 min\n    role-play, 15 min debrief. Mastery is certified in live calls, not in the classroom.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
   "slug": "module-key-what-each-box-means",
   "title": "Module Key — What Each Box Means",
   "html": "<h3 id=\"legend\">Module Key &mdash; What Each Box Means</h3>\n\n<p>The visual taxonomy is the same one you already know from the Advisor Training System. Use it as a learning\nshortcut: the color tells the brain what kind of thinking to do.</p>\n\n<div class=\"callout c-script\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">SCRIPT</span><span class=\"title\">The exact words.</span>\n  <p>Memorize tone, not just text. Never paraphrase the close.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout c-decoder\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">PSYCHOLOGY DECODER</span><span class=\"title\">Why it works on the human brain.</span>\n  <p>Master this and you stop sounding scripted. This is the unlock.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout c-drill\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">DRILL</span><span class=\"title\">A practice rep.</span>\n  <p>Run with a partner or with the AI. Reps build instinct; instinct survives pressure.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout c-mastery\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">MASTERY CHECK</span><span class=\"title\">The gate to the next level.</span>\n  <p>Observable behaviors in live calls. Pass = promotion.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout c-stop\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">STOP</span><span class=\"title\">A hard gate.</span>\n  <p>Do not advance until the action is complete. These exist because skipping them has cost real sales.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout c-protip\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">PRO TIP</span><span class=\"title\">A veteran shortcut.</span>\n  <p>Earned the hard way so you don&rsquo;t have to.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout c-coach\">\n  <span class=\"tag\">COACH&rsquo;S CORNER</span><span class=\"title\">How to coach this step.</span>\n  <p>What to listen for, what to score, what to praise, what to correct.</p>\n</div>"
  }
 ]
}